Stamford.Five Mile River Landing Historic Distric: The Five Mile River Landing Historic District in the Rowayton section of Norwalk, Connecticut is a historic district that was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 2009. It extends along Rowayton Street from Witch Lane to Pennoyer Street, and includes all of the properties on the latter as well. The area was a major local center of the shipping industry in the 19th century.
